  <brief_title>Perampanel for Sporadic Amyotrophic Lateral Sclerosis (ALS)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Perampanel for Sporadic Amyotrophic Lateral Sclerosis (ALS): A Multicenter, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Parallel-group Phase 2 Trials</official_title>
