  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To investigate the safety and the efficacy of perampanel in patients with sporadic
      amyotrophic lateral sclerosis
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the effect of peramanel for 48 weeks on progression of disease in subjects with
      ALS, as measured by ALS Functional Rating Scale-Revised (ALSFRS-R)
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
